items.title: SpaceX didn’t properly inspect crane before collapse at Starbase, OSHA says

items.title: China’s Renewable Energy Revolution Is a Huge Mess That Might Save the World

items.description: Explosive acceleration, limited dexterity, eyes in the back of its head. What could possibly go wrong?
